## Modified Signup Flow

### BEFORE (Old Flow):
```
User fills form → Submit → Account created → Trial starts → Dashboard
```

### AFTER (New Flow):
```
User fills form 
  → Validate form
  → Check duplicate email
  → Generate OTP
  → Send OTP email
  → Show OTP Panel
    → User enters OTP
    → Verify OTP
    → ✓ OTP Correct: Create account → Trial starts → Dashboard
    → ✗ OTP Wrong: Show error, allow retry
    → ✗ OTP Expired: Show error, allow resend
  → User can go back to form if needed
```

---

## Key Features

✅ **Email Verification Required** — Ensures email ownership
✅ **OTP Expiration** — 5-minute timer prevents abuse
✅ **Resend Functionality** — Users can request new OTP
✅ **Back Button** — Users can go back to correct email
✅ **Dev Mode** — OTP displays on screen if email not configured
✅ **Duplicate Email Check** — Prevents duplicate accounts
✅ **Proper Cleanup** — OTP state resets when closing modal
✅ **Trial System Preserved** — Trial still starts after account creation
✅ **Dashboard Redirect** — Takes user to dashboard after verification

