## Integration with EmailJS

The implementation uses the same EmailJS approach as your existing forgot password feature:
- Uses browser-side initialization with `emailjs.init()`
- Sends emails via browser with `emailjs.send()`
- Gracefully falls back to dev mode if keys not configured

Template variables expected by EmailJS:
- `{{to_email}}` — User's email address
- `{{first_name}}` — User's first name
- `{{otp_code}}` — The 6-digit OTP code

---

## What Happens If EmailJS Not Configured

If keys are left as `'YOUR_..._HERE'`:
- User can still test signup flow
- OTP displays on screen in dev mode
- Shows message: "Your OTP (dev mode): 123456"
- Perfect for local development

